text: Rumer Glenn Willis (born August 16, 1988 ) is an American actress. She has been featured in several movies. She was born in Paducah, Kentucky. She is the eldest daughter of actors Demi Moore and Bruce Willis, and the eldest sister of Scout Willis and Tallulah Willis. On April 18, 2023, Willis would give birth to her daughter Louetta. She would separate from her partner Derek Richard Thomas in 2024. ==References== == Other websites == * Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Kentucky Category:People from Paducah, Kentucky Category:American child actors Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors
